From: Christoph Hellwig <hch@lst.de>
Date: Mon, 24 Jan 2022 10:11:06 +0100
Subject: [PATCH] block: pass a block_device and opf to bio_init
Git-commit: 49add4966d79244013fce35f95c6833fae82b8b1
Patch-mainline: v5.18-rc1
References: jsc#PED-1183

Pass the block_device that we plan to use this bio for and the
operation to bio_init to optimize the assignment.  A NULL block_device
can be passed, both for the passthrough case on a raw request_queue and
to temporarily avoid refactoring some nasty code.

